Following is a list of most useful c++ idioms
@see http://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/More_C%2B%2B_Idioms

0.virtual functions => Letting old code call new code at runtime

1.templates         => Letting old code call new code at compile time

2.RAII => Resource Acquisition Is Initialization

3.Pimpl => Pointer To Implementation

4.Checked delete => Increase safety of delete expression
